body:
`protobuf-3.0.0-cp3-none-any.whl` is supported according to `pep425` tags for `pip  8.1.2`, so renaming hack should work :)
Looks like we might need to rebuild these packages if we want to pass them through `auditwheel`, as `cp3-none-linux_x86_64` is still not a supported tag.
